    <title>玩客云openwrt配置DDNS-GO</title>
    <url>/undefined/b7d6c1e4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>打开docker拉取镜像jeess&#x2F;ddns-go:v6.6.3</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-1.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-1"></p>
<p>打开容器点击添加，更改容器名字，容器镜像选择刚才的的ddnsgo镜像，其他默认保存即可</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-2.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-2"></p>
<p>然后访问openwrt的ip加9876端口号例如192.168.1.1:9876，进入网站默认直接登陆即可，进入后更改用户名和密码。</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-3.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-3"></p>
<p>然后开始配置dns域名解析服务，我这里使用的是dnspod，创建dnspod token，点击蓝色按钮会自动跳转到密钥创建界面</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-4.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-4"></p>
<p>进入dnspod后点击创建密钥，自行创建即可不过多介绍，记得保存好id和token。</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-5.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-5"></p>
<p>在这里填入id和token，TLL选择自动即可</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-6.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-6"></p>
<p>ipv4如果有公网可以打开，我这里没有就关闭了</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-7.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-7"></p>
<p>ipv6勾选，选择通过网卡获取，一般是第一个地址，这里匹配正则表达式填入@1，Domains填入你要解析的域名</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-8.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-8"></p>
<p>这里ddns-go就配置完成了，当然你如果想要解析通知的话可以配置一下webhook，我这里使用的飞书机器人，当然你如果想使用其他的推送可以点击蓝色按钮，有更多介绍。</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-9.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-9"></p>
<p>这里以飞书为例打开飞书创建群组，名字随意，创建好后点击群头像选择群机器人</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-10.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-10"></p>
<p>点击添加机器人</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-11.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-11"></p>
<p>选择自定义机器人</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-12.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-12"></p>
<p>选择后点击添加</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-13.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-13"></p>
<p>这里复制一下飞书机器人的webhook地址，自定义关键词一定要打开，填入“你的公网IP变了”</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-14.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-14"></p>
<p>然后点击完成即可…</p>
<p>把刚才复制的机器人webhook地址填入url里面</p>
<p><img src="https://image.mrarub.eu.org/image/2024/b7d6c1e4-15.webp" alt="b7d6c1e4-15"></p>
<p>把这行代码粘贴到RequestBody里面</p>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;msg_type&quot;: &quot;post&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;content&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;post&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;zh_cn&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                &quot;title&quot;: &quot;你的公网IP变了&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">                &quot;content&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">                    [</span><br><span class="line">                        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;text&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">                            &quot;text&quot;: &quot;IPv6地址：#&#123;ipv6Addr&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    ],</span><br><span class="line">                    [</span><br><span class="line">                        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;text&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">                            &quot;text&quot;: &quot;域名更新结果：#&#123;ipv6Result&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    ]</span><br><span class="line">                ]</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Headrs为空</p>
<p>点击模拟测试webhook按钮，飞书机器人就发通知了</p>
<p>DDNS-GO的配置就完结了</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>玩客云</category>
      </categories>
  </entry>
